Symbol.Script_3D:
! Tea Kettle.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 6
if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
HOTSPOT 0,0,0 HOTSPOT H,0,0 HOTSPOT 0,H,0 HOTSPOT -H,0,0 HOTSPOT 0,-H,0
HOTSPOT -x1,0,z1 HOTSPOT H*1.25+H/8,0,0 HOTSPOT 0,0,H*1.25+H/8
Resol 2.5*gs_resol Material kettle_mat Ellips H, H Roty -45 Addz H-H/32 Resol 1.5*gs_resol Cone H/2, H/8, H/16, 90, 90 Material ac_mat Addz H/2 Cone H/16, H/16, H/18, 90, 90 Del 3 Material ac_mat Resol gs_resol Arme H*1.26, H, H/32, H*0.99, 0 Addz H/32 Roty 90 Material ac_mat addy 0.004 Arme H*1.26, H, H/32, H*0.99, -H/32 del 1 Material handle_mat Addx -H*1.25-H/32 Resol 3*gs_resol Elbow H*1.25+H/16, 90, H/16 Addz -H/16 Material ac_mat Cylind H/16, H/16 del 4 End
Symbol.Script_2D:
!!Tea Kettle.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, H, 0, 1, -0.0, 0.0, 900, H, 180, 4001, 0.0, 0.0, 900, H, 180, 4001
LINE2 0,0,H*1.25+H/8,0 LINE2 -x1,0,-31/32*H*sin(45),H/8 LINE2 -x1,0,-31/32*H*sin(45),-H/8
HOTSPOT2 0,0 HOTSPOT2 H*1.25+H/8,0 HOTSPOT2 0,H HOTSPOT2 -x1,0 HOTSPOT2 0,-H
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
H=B/2
x1=49/32*H*sin(45)+1/18*H*sin(45) !!POINT -a(max),0 z1=49/32*H*sin(45)-1/18*H*sin(45) !! max.HEIGHT
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values "gs_resol" range [6,)
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=7 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
parameters a=(49/32*H*sin(45)+1/18*H*sin(45))+(H*1.25+H/8) parameters ZZYZX=H*1.25+H/8
lock "a","zzyzx"
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
